### Task Manager API - REST Client Tests
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code

### Variables
@baseUrl_local = http://localhost:3000
@baseUrl_render = https://your-app-name.onrender.com
@contentType = application/json

### Use local for development
@baseUrl = {{baseUrl_local}}

### Uncomment line below to test production on Render
# @baseUrl = {{baseUrl_render}}

###############################################
### ROOT ENDPOINT
###############################################

### Get API Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###############################################
### GET REQUESTS
###############################################

### Get all tasks
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### Get task by ID (replace with actual task ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###############################################
### POST REQUESTS
###############################################

### Create new task
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Complete assignment",
  "description": "Finish the task manager API project",
  "status": "pending",
  "dueDate": "2025-11-15"
}

### Create another task
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Study for exam",
